name: Github-travis-addon
body:
### Github Travis Addon for Firefox

This addon allows you to track what is happening on your your Travis CI builds. You can either visit the page or have a panel in your addon bar.

This is simplifying the way that you use Travis CI daily!
tagline: Firefox addon that allows you to track Travis CI projects
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
